Tim Hovey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tim_Hovey 0 Tim Hovey (June 19, 1945 – September 9, 1989) was a former American child actor during the 1950s. He later became a musician, road manager and an audio engineer for rock bands. Tim_Hovey ( June_19_,_1945 – September_9_,_1989 ) was a_former_American_child_actor during the_1950s .
